            "question": {
                "text": "Suppose we are given n keys, m hash table slots, and \ntwo simple uniform hash functions h1 and h2 . Further \nsuppose our hashing scheme uses h1 for the odd keys \nand h2 for the even keys. What is the expected \nnumber of keys in a slot?",
